<style>
    .module-image iframe {
        width: 53vw;
    }
</style>
<div class="page-header centered">
    <h2 class="page-title">Heavy Metal Pollution Awareness</h2>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Understanding, monitoring, and preventing water contamination</p>
</div>

<div class="education-layout">
    <div class="modules-sidebar">
        <h3 class="sidebar-title">Learning Modules</h3>
        <div class="modules-list">
            <a href="/education?module=metals&lang=<%= language %>"
                class="module-item <%= activeModule === 'metals' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <div class="module-content">
                    <h4 class="module-title">Introduction to Heavy Metals</h4>
                    <p class="module-description">Types, sources, and health impacts</p>
                    <div class="module-meta">
                        <span class="duration">15 min</span>
                        <span class="status completed">Completed</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/education?module=indices&lang=<%= language %>"
                class="module-item <%= activeModule === 'indices' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <div class="module-content">
                    <h4 class="module-title">Pollution Indices</h4>
                    <p class="module-description">Understanding Water Quality Index & Heavy Metal Pollution Index</p>
                    <div class="module-meta">
                        <span class="duration">20 min</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/education?module=solutions&lang=<%= language %>"
                class="module-item <%= activeModule === 'solutions' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <div class="module-content">
                    <h4 class="module-title">Prevention & Solutions</h4>
                    <p class="module-description">Mitigation strategies and sustainable practices</p>
                    <div class="module-meta">
                        <span class="duration">10 min</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-content-area">
        <div class="module-header">
            <h3 class="module-active-title">
                <% if (activeModule==='metals' ) { %>Introduction to Heavy Metals<% } %>
                <% if (activeModule==='indices' ) { %>Pollution Indices<% } %>
                <% if (activeModule==='solutions' ) { %>Prevention & Solutions<% } %>
            </h3>
            <div class="module-actions">
                <button class="action-btn primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
                    Start Module
                </button>
                <button class="action-btn secondary">
                    <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
                    Download
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="module-body">
            <% if (activeModule==='metals' ) { %>
                <div class="module-image">
                    <iframe width="560" height="315"
                        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9MuBzW7pWtk?start=0&autoplay=0&controls=1&rel=0&modestbranding=1"
                        frameborder="0" allow="autoplay" allowfullscreen>
                    </iframe>
                </div>
                <div class="module-text">
                    <p>Heavy metals such as lead, arsenic, cadmium, and mercury pose a serious threat to human health
                        and aquatic ecosystems. Learn about:</p>
                    <ul class="steps-list">
                        <li>Sources of heavy metal pollution (industrial, agricultural, domestic)</li>
                        <li>Bioaccumulation and long-term effects on health</li>
                        <li>Impact on children, vulnerable communities, and environment</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <% if (activeModule==='indices' ) { %>
                <div class="module-image">
                    <img src="/images/pollution-index.jpg" alt="Pollution indices concept" class="content-image">
                </div>
                <div class="module-text">
                    <p>Pollution indices provide a scientific way to assess contamination levels. Key indices include:</p>
                    <ul class="steps-list">
                        <li><b>Water Quality Index (WQI):</b> Overall measure of water suitability</li>
                        <li><b>Heavy Metal Pollution Index (HPI):</b> Composite score based on toxic metals</li>
                        <li><b>Metal Index (MI):</b> Identifies degree of contamination</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <% if (activeModule==='solutions' ) { %>
                <div class="module-image">
                    <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/924824/pexels-photo-924824.jpeg"
                        alt="Clean water solutions" class="content-image">
                </div>
                <div class="module-text">
                    <p>Solutions require combined effort of technology and community action. Focus areas include:</p>
                    <div class="warning-box">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Sustainable Solutions</h4>
                        <ul class="warning-list">
                            <li>AI-powered monitoring applications for real-time water analysis</li>
                            <li>Regular testing and pollution index evaluation</li>
                            <li>Community participation in safe water practices</li>
                            <li>Policy-driven interventions and stricter regulation</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="community-impact">
            <div class="impact-header">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                <h4>Community Impact</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="impact-stats">
                <div class="impact-stat">
                    <div class="impact-number">1,200+</div>
                    <div class="impact-label">Samples Analyzed</div>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-stat">
                    <div class="impact-number">80+</div>
                    <div class="impact-label">Communities Reached</div>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-stat">
                    <div class="impact-number">72%</div>
                    <div class="impact-label">Improved Water Safety</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        initializeEducation();
    });
</script>
